Atoms are the smallest component units, for example a button or an input.
These do not keep state, but receive properties.
Input or units that display focus events or animations can be created with React.forwardRef.
https://pt-br.reactjs.org/docs/forwarding-refs.html#forwarding-refs-to-dom-components
